## 5. Limitations
The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of manipulation as a form of abuse. The findings are limited to the perspectives and data provided by the selected sources. Further research, including empirical studies and expert interviews, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic. Additionally, cultural and contextual differences in the perception of manipulation and abuse were not extensively explored in this report.